[{"id":"3b2344d9b60afcaf5d7f43fc50b09c04","from":"Best of All Worlds","from_email":"erikw@bestofallworlds.com","to":"jeeproject@yahoo.com","to_list":[{"name":"jeeproject@yahoo.com","email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com"}],"cc_list":[],"subject":"A quick update from Best of All Worlds","date":"2014-02-17T19:05:10.000Z","formatted_date":"Feb 17, 2014","formatted_time":"7:05 PM","body":"Email not displaying correctly? View it ( http://sendgrid.org/wf/webmail?rp=ZTI1bGQzTnNaWFIwWlhKZmFXUTZNVEl6TkN4MWMyVnlYMmxrT2pJMU5qVTBmUWV5SnVaWGR6YkdWMGRHVnlYMmxrSWpvaU1qVXdPREUwTWlJc0ltNWxkM05zWlhSMFpYSmZkWE5sY2w5cFpDSTZOREk0TkRnMk9UYzROVGQ5 ) in your browser\n\nDear\u00a0Jeffrey,\n\n\nHere is a quick update from Best of All Worlds (BOAW ( http://bestofallworlds.com )).\n\u00a0\nWe are now ready to finalize fixes and improvements to the site and the iPhone app. We have received lots of great feedback and can\u2019t wait to implement them and to have BOAW reach its full potential in the coming months.\n\u00a0\nWe have been operating on limited resources, and we are in process of raising additional funds in the coming weeks. We have initiated a crowdfunding campaign on Crowdcube.com ( http://crowdcube.com ) in the UK. This crowdfunding allows for individuals and entities to invest in BOAW. We see this as a complement to our private fundraising efforts and also as a way to broaden our base of stakeholders around the world. Please see our pitch on http://bit.ly/boawoffer ( http://bit.ly/boawoffer ).\n\u00a0\nWe have a strong platform built with the latest technology and a user interface that will be significantly improved with relatively modest resources. As we are still in \u201cPrivate Beta\u201d, we have not encouraged new invitations until we have done the next release. We expect user engagement to increase significantly, and in particular once we start growing the community beyond its currently modest size.\n\u00a0\nWe strongly believe in our unique market positioning to offer members to interact in a trusted environment and find new opportunities around their passions. We are looking forward to a positive momentum going and that you all want to join us! US News and World Report just summed it up nicely in the article with the title \u201cFilling the Facebook Gap\u201d!\n\u00a0\nhttp://www.usnews.com/opinion/economic-intelligence/2014/02/06/how-private-social-networks-can-compete-with-facebook ( http://www.usnews.com/opinion/economic-intelligence/2014/02/06/how-private-social-networks-can-compete-with-facebook )\n\u00a0\nAgain, thanks for all your feedback, and see you online soon!\n\u00a0\n\nWarm regards,\nErik\n\nTo unsubscribe, please go\u00a0here ( https://www.bestofallworlds.com/?unsubscribe=true&invite_code=[Code] ).Best of All Worlds AB, Sturegatan 56, Stockholm, Sweden 11436","body_html":"<style type=\"text/css\">.ReadMsgBody{width:100%;}.ExternalClass{width:100%;}span.yshortcuts{color:#000;background-color:none;border:none;}span.yshortcuts:hover,span.yshortcuts:active,span.yshortcuts:focus{color:#000;background-color:none;border:none;}p{margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;}*{-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;}</style><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse;background:#ddd;min-width:620px;table-layout:fixed;\"><tbody><tr><td align=\"center\" style=\"padding-right:10px;padding-top:10px;padding-bottom:10px;padding-left:10px;\"><div style=\"width:auto;margin-right:auto;margin-left:auto;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;color:#000;font-family:Arial;font-size:12px;line-height:150%;\"><table style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:separate;table-layout:fixed;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td align=\"center\"><table width=\"600\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:0px;table-layout:fixed;width:600px;background:#FFFFFF;\"><tbody><tr><td><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"width:600px;border-collapse:collapse;tab