rivate Beta&rdquo;, we have not encouraged new invitations until we have done the next release. We expect user engagement to increase significantly, and in particular once we start growing the community beyond its currently modest size.<br />\n\t&nbsp;<br />\n\tWe strongly believe in our unique market positioning to offer members to interact in a trusted environment and find new opportunities around their passions. We are looking forward to a positive momentum going and that you all want to join us! US News and World Report just summed it up nicely in the article with the title &ldquo;Filling the Facebook Gap&rdquo;!<br />\n\t&nbsp;<br />\n\t<a href=\"http://mail.bestofallworlds.com/wf/click?upn=Oxx4Z5iBg2B5tY-2BdcBqwz9B-2FK1fA16qPzn2y0dnGalGp-2Bq-2Fab99Ap9ZJgLB0RluCgtXJHf3UGT3GukAj1pj7b7gdOUoGyWSlxharW0qRIpwP-2BygAPtVCj3UAxuecO4WauKkeT1HCz2oZcPyE-2BpXtlBHEEfF1TgrcYgT21uA6k3g-3D_geZW8XjBK0GzFIAPwf148zsDvsjcKJ9D7yyzJM-2FoN7SUIxaspqC100QQW8ShwadyAvyGRsk4l7yFkiuVb5MI0Q1WXJ9I5dbbRVPfpg9Rci-2F0LtZLWOM3bJU4vQEoedBJkGNGA7REHRuYOhNG3oJSKcCNvl1CjzoPtFQwYeaMRoa-2FlhGaK77rg4bBl9tymTeUPzW7it9V7n5RNM8gR3NPbF2shjg-2FV0Y527YInUEQWBUYLwA7dirBqgnKZa9TlkckHLlcURJS3c1dsbBPWPDmkuFNmv7-2Bml7VwRfGNs0S1qXnKJ6paMYzwcVajBf-2BnTEMxeFaOY8nnQfbEjXdft6bb3GQ-2FRqumavolwdYu7-2FY-2B4OCFInIQvpVQQnNCpcqHEa-2Bn5R94NJAra3MMY5H8ZeFJg-3D-3D\"><strong>http://www.usnews.com/opinion/economic-intelligence/2014/02/06/how-private-social-networks-can-compete-with-facebook</strong></a><br />\n\t&nbsp;<br />\n\tAgain, thanks for all your feedback, and see you online soon!<br />\n\t&nbsp;<br />\n\t<br />\n\tWarm regards,<br />\n\tErik</span></span></p>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div><table style=\"border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:0px;table-layout:fixed;\" cellpadding=\"5\" cellspacing=\"5\"><tbody><tr><td></td></tr></tbody></table><table style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:separate;table-layout:fixed;background:#f1f1f1;\" cellspacing=\"15\" cellpadding=\"0\"><tbody><tr